'Trade_Invitation', '*WHO*,<p>\r\n\r\nAs one of last year\'s traders at *FESTIVAL*, you\'re being given an advance opportunity to book a pitch this for *PLANYEAR* before we open booking to everyone.  <p>\r\n\r\nThe dates are *DATES*.<p>\r\n\r\nThe location you are being offered is *LOCATION* at a price of *PRICE*.<p>\r\n\r\nIf you wish to accept the offer of a pitch at the quoted price, go to your personal *LINK* and click \'accept\'.<p>\r\n\r\nShortly after accepting the offer, you will be sent an invoice for a deposit.  To secure the pitch, you must pay your deposit promptly.<p>\r\n\r\nIf you wish to decline the offer, please click on your personal link and click \'decline\'. <p>\r\n\r\nPlease do NOT address any queries to our treasurer unless they are related to payments.  She\'s a very busy woman.  The trade address *MAILTO_trade* will reach Moe who can help you with everything else, including requests for a different location.<p>\r\n\r\nIf you are no longer trading, or no longer wish to be notified about trade stands at the festival click *REMOVE*.<p>\r\n  \r\nThis year, we will be featuring all our traders on our web site.\r\n\r\nPlease use this personal *LINK* to directly upload a photo of your stand/products and to write about what you sell.<p>\r\n\r\nYou can also use this link to add/correct details about your business, contact information, or change your pitch(es) , give power requirements, update your Insurance and Risk Assessment etc.<p>\r\n\r\nPhotos and descriptions of your goods will be visible to the public. Personal information can only be seen by the festival committee.<p>  \r\n  \r\nDetails of your pitch number, general trader information and particulars of setup and cleardown\r\ninformation will  appear later and be visible through the link.<p>\r\n\r\nSave the link for future use.  If you lose or forget it you will be able to request a new personal link\r\nfrom the website (as soon as trade applications go public).<p>\r\n\r\nIf you have any queries that are not answered by the <a href=http://*HOST*/int/TradeFAQ.php>Trade FAQ</a>,\r\nplease contact *MAILTO_trade*.<p>\r\n\r\n'
'Trade_Open', '*WHO*,<p>\r\n  \r\nTrade stand booking for the *FESTIVAL* in *PLANYEAR* is now open.<p>\r\n    \r\nPlease use this personal *LINK* to directly add and/or correct details about your business, contact information,\r\nyour product descriptions, book or change your pitch(es) and give power requirements, update your\r\nInsurance and Risk Assessment etc.<p>\r\n  \r\nDetails of your pitch location, general trader information and particulars of setup and cleardown\r\ninformation will also appear through the link.<p> \r\n    \r\nSave the link for future use.  If you lose or forget it you will be able to request a new personal link\r\nfrom the website (as soon as trade appliactions go public).<p>\r\n  \r\nIf you have any queries that are not answered by the <a href=http://*HOST*/int/TradeFAQ.php>Trade FAQ</a>,\r\nplease contact *MAILTO_trade*.<p>\r\n  \r\nIf you are no longer trading, or no longer wish to be notified about trade stands at the festival click *REMOVE*.<p>\r\n'
'Trade_Link', '*WHO*,<p>\r\n\r\nPlease use this *LINK*.<p>\r\n\r\nTo add/correct details about your business, contact information, your product descriptions, pitch and power requirements,\r\nupdate your Insurance and Risk Assessment etc.<p>\r\n\r\nDetails of your pitch location, general trader information and particulars of setup and clear down information will also appear there.<p>\r\n\r\nSave the link for future use.<p>'
'Trade_Submit', '*WHO*,<p>\r\n\r\nThankyou for submitting your application for Trading at the *FESTIVAL* in *PLANYEAR*.<p>\r\n\r\nPlease use this *LINK* to add/correct details about your business, contact information, your product descriptions, book or change your pitch(es) and give\r\npower requirements, update your Insurance and Risk Assessment etc.<p> \r\n\r\nDetails of your pitch location, general trader information and particulars of setup and clear down information will also appear there.<p>\r\nSave the link for future use.<p>\r\n\r\nYou should have a response within 7 days to tell you if your application has been successful.\r\n\r\nIf you have any queries that are not answered by the <a href=http://*HOST*/int/TradeFAQ.php>Trade FAQ</a>,\r\nplease contact *MAILTO_trade*<p>\r\n\r\n*DETAILS*'
'Trade_InvitationBetter', '*WHO*,<p>\r\n\r\nAs one of last year\'s traders at *FESTIVAL*, you\'re being given an advance opportunity to book a pitch this for *PLANYEAR* before we open booking to everyone.  <p>\r\n\r\nThe location we originally gave you last year was an area we hadn\'t previously used for trade stands, and was offered at a low price because it was an unknown.  The  offer we are making here is for the area you were moved to on Sunday, but the price is the price is the price for the new area and hence will be higher than the rate you paid last year.<p>\r\n\r\nThe dates are *DATES*.<p>\r\n\r\nThe location you are being offered is *LOCATION* at a price of *PRICE*.<p>\r\n\r\nIf you wish to accept the offer of a pitch at the quoted price, go to your personal *LINK* and click \'accept\'.<p>\r\n\r\nShortly after accepting the offer, you will be sent an invoice for a deposit.  To secure the pitch, you must pay your deposit promptly.<p>\r\n\r\n\r\nIf you wish to decline the offer, please click on your personal link and click \'decline\'. <p>\r\n\r\nPlease do NOT address any queries to our treasurer unless they are related to payments.  She\'s a very busy woman.  The trade address *MAILTO_trade* will reach Moe who can help you with everything else, including requests for a different location.<p>\r\n\r\nIf you are no longer trading, or no longer wish to be notified about trade stands at the festival click *REMOVE*.<p>\r\n  \r\nThis year, we will be featuring all our traders on our web site.\r\n\r\nPlease use this personal *LINK* to directly upload a photo of your stand/products and to write about what you sell.<p>\r\n\r\nYou can also use this link to add/correct details about your business, contact information, or change your pitch(es) , give power requirements, update your Insurance and Risk Assessment etc.<p>\r\n\r\nPhotos and descriptions of your goods will be visible to the public. Personal information can only be seen by the festival committee.<p>  \r\n  \r\nDetails of your pitch number, general trader information and particulars of setup and cleardown\r\ninformation will  appear later and be visible through the link.<p>\r\n\r\nSave the link for future use.  If you lose or forget it you will be able to request a new personal link\r\nfrom the website (as soon as trade applications go public).<p>\r\n\r\nIf you have any queries that are not answered by the <a href=http://*HOST*/int/TradeFAQ.php>Trade FAQ</a>,\r\nplease contact *MAILTO_trade*.<p>\r\n\r\n'
'Login_Welcome', '*WHO*,<p>\r\n\r\nWelcome to the *FESTIVAL* staff pages.<p>\r\n\r\nIt is initially accessed by using the <a href=https://*HOST*/int/Login.php>Login</a> at the bottom of any page below the copyright statement on any page of the \r\n<a href=https://*HOST*>website</a>.<p>\r\n\r\nYour username is : *USER*<br>\r\nInitial password : *PWD*<p>\r\n\r\nWhen you are logged in, an extra tab will appear on the navigation bar \'Staff Tools\' this gives access to the Database, Timeline and Document storage.<p>\r\n\r\n'
'Trade_AcceptNoDeposit', '*WHO*,<p>\r\n\r\nThis is to confirm that you have accepted our offer to trade at *FESTIVAL* in *PLANYEAR*.<p>\r\n\r\nThe trade address *MAILTO_trade* will reach Moe who can help you with everything else, including requests for a different location.  <p> \r\n\r\nPlease use this *LINK* to add/correct details about your business, contact information, your product descriptions, book or change your pitch(es) and give\r\npower requirements, update your Insurance and Risk Assessment etc.<p> \r\n\r\nDetails of your pitch location, general trader information and particulars of setup and clear down information will also appear there.<p>\r\n\r\n<b>Save the link for future use.</b><p>\r\n\r\n*DETAILS*'
'Trade_Cancel', '*WHO*,<p>\r\n\r\nThis is to record that your application for trading at *FESTIVAL* in *PLANYEAR* has been cancelled.<p>\r\n\r\nIf this is in error please contact *MAILTO_trade*.<p>\r\n\r\nYou may use your *LINK* to apply again in the future.<p>\r\n\r\nIf you are no longer trading, or no longer wish to be notified about trade stands at the festival click *REMOVE*.<p>\r\n'
'Trade_Hold', '*WHO*,<p>\r\n\r\nYour application to trade at the *FESTIVAL* in *PLANYEAR*, is being held on the wait list. <p>\r\n\r\nif space is found we hope to offer you a pitch.<p>\r\n\r\nPlease use this *LINK* to add/correct details about your business, contact information, your product descriptions, book or change your pitch(es) and give\r\npower requirements, update your Insurance and Risk Assessment etc.<p> \r\n\r\nIf you have any queries that are not answered by the <a href=http://*HOST*/int/TradeFAQ.php>Trade FAQ</a>,\r\nplease contact *MAILTO_trade*<p>\r\n'
