'Trade_RequestDeposit', 'Mandy,<p>\r\n\r\nThe Trader below has accepted the offer of a pitch/pitches and should be invoiced for their deposit of &pound;*DEPOSIT* now.<p>\r\n\r\nThe balance will be &pound;*BALANCE*, if this changes, eg because of power requests or a change of pitch, we will immediately inform you.<p>\r\n\r\nDirect link to that trader *WMFFLINK* (you need to be logged in for this to work)\r\n\r\n*DETAILS*'
