'Trade_NewSubmit', 'Moe,<p>\r\n\r\nThe trader below has submitted an application, please either: decline, hold, or quote them a fee.<p>\r\n\r\nDirect link to that trader *WMFFLINK* (you need to be logged in for this to work)\r\n\r\n*DETAILS*'
'Trade_Quote', '*WHO*,<p>\r\n\r\nYou requested a trade stall pitch for the *PLANYEAR* *FESTIVAL* and we\'re pleased to say that we\'d love to have you.<p>\r\n\r\nThe location you are being offered is *LOCATION* at a price of *PRICE*.<p>\r\n\r\nPlease use this *LINK* accept the quote.\r\n\r\nThe link can also be used to add/correct details about your business, contact information, your product descriptions, book or change your pitch(es) and give\r\npower requirements, update your Insurance and Risk Assessment etc.<p> \r\n\r\nDetails of your pitch location, general trader information and particulars of setup and clear down information will also appear there.<p>\r\n\r\nSave the link for future use.<p>\r\n\r\nIf you have any queries that are not answered by the <a href=http://*HOST*/int/TradeFAQ.php>Trade FAQ</a>,\r\nplease contact *MAILTO_trade*<p>'
'Trade_Artisan_Invite', '*WHO*,<p>\r\n\r\n*FESTIVAL* is developing an exciting opportunity for artisan traders in *PLANYEAR*! <p>\r\n\r\nWe want to bring you into the heart of the festival, with a new dedicated marquee on Willow Walk (opposite the Waitrose store). <p>\r\n\r\nYear after year, Willow Walk is the vibrant centre of the festival for families, with a real buzz around the youth stage and food outlets catering for all tastes. <p>\r\n\r\nThis year, a limited number of local artisan traders will have space to display and sell their wares, as well as demonstrate their skills and services through optional workshops in our demo zone. <p>\r\n\r\nWe would like to offer you trading in *LOCATION* on *DATES* at the price of just *PRICE*. <p>\r\n\r\nWe will provide you with a 6ft x 2.5ft table, which you may cover and dress as you please. We would also like to offer you the chance to give timetabled workshops and/or demos in our new Demo zone, along with a listing in our official *FESTIVAL* programme. <p>\r\n\r\nIf you wish to accept the offer of a pitch at the quoted price, go to your personal *LINK* and click \'accept\'.<p>\r\n\r\nShortly after accepting the offer, you will be sent an invoice for a deposit, which should be paid promptly to secure your pitch.<p>\r\n\r\nIf you wish to decline the offer, please click on your personal link and click \'decline\'. <p>\r\n\r\nFor all queries and questions, please contact your dedicated Artisan Trade coordinator at *MAILTO_craft*. <p>\r\n\r\nIf you are no longer trading, or no longer wish to be notified about trade stands at the festival click *REMOVE*.<p>\r\n  \r\nThis year, we will be featuring all our traders on our web site.\r\n\r\nPlease use this personal *LINK* to directly upload a photo of your stand/products and to write about what you sell.<p>\r\n\r\nYou can also use this link to add/correct details about your business, contact information, or change your pitch(es) , give power requirements, update your Insurance and Risk Assessment etc.<p>\r\n\r\nPhotos and descriptions of your goods will be visible to the public. Personal information can only be seen by the festival committee.<p>  \r\n  \r\nDetails of your pitch number, general trader information and particulars of setup and cleardown\r\ninformation will  appear later and be visible through the link.<p>\r\n\r\nSave the link for future use.  If you lose or forget it you will be able to request a new personal link\r\nfrom the website.<p>\r\n\r\nIf you have any queries that are not answered by the <a href=http://*HOST*/int/TradeFAQ.php>Trade FAQ</a>,\r\nplease contact *MAILTO_craft*.<p>\r\n'
'Trade_Artisan_Accept', '*WHO*,<p>\r\n\r\nThis is to confirm that you have accepted our offer to trade as an Artisan at *FESTIVAL* in *PLANYEAR*. <p>\r\n\r\nYou should receive an invoice in a few days asking you to pay your deposit of *DEPOSIT*. Later next year you will receive a second invoice to pay the balance of *BALANCE*. <p>\r\n\r\nFor any further queries, please contact your Artisan Trade at *MAILTO_craft*.<p> \r\n\r\nPlease use this *LINK* to add/correct details about your business, contact information, your product descriptions, book or change your pitch(es), and update your Insurance and Risk Assessment etc. <p>\r\n\r\nDetails of your pitch location, general trader information and particulars of setup and clear down information will also appear there. <p>\r\n\r\nKind Regards <p>\r\n\r\n Artisan Trade Co-ordinators.\r\n\r\n'
'Login_Forgot_Password', '*WHO*,<p>\r\n\r\nHere is a limited duration temporary *LINK* to set a new password (it will only work for a few hours).<p>'
'Trade_Accepted_FullInvoice', '*WHO*,<p>\r\n\r\nThis is to confirm that you have accepted our offer to trade at *FESTIVAL* in *PLANYEAR*.<p>\r\n\r\nAttached is an invoice for the full amount of *PRICE*, please pay this promptly to secure your pitch.<p>\r\n\r\nThe trade address *MAILTO_trade* will reach Moe who can help you with everything else, including requests for a different location.<p> \r\n\r\nPlease use this *LINK* to add/correct details about your business, contact information, your product descriptions, book or change your pitch(es) and give\r\npower requirements, update your Insurance and Risk Assessment etc.<p> \r\n\r\nDetails of your pitch location, general trader information and particulars of setup and clear down information will also appear there.<p>\r\n\r\n<b>Save the link for future use.</b><p>\r\n\r\n*DETAILS*'
